name: custom design
description:
Want something unique made especially for you? Here's your chance! 

Once you purchase this design, please e-mail me at tangiblelovedesigns@gmail.com with the photograph(s) you would like included and any information that can help me in the design of your card (e.g., color, wording, or size preferences). The more specific you are, the better I am able to meet your wishes! If you have a particular vision, let me know. Otherwise I will create a one-of-a-kind card and then send you the completed design for your approval within 1-2 business days.
